extendedInfo.description: The Chicago Dental Society Midwinter Meeting (sm), offers three full days of continuing dental education provided by 125 clinicians for all members of the dental team, with over 690 exhibiting companies sharing the latest in dental products and services every year at McCormick Place West in Chicago. Over 31,000 attendees participate in this annual February dental convention. The Chicago Dental Society Midwinter Meeting (sm) is among the top 50 largest medical meetings in the country annually.Keywords: Chicago Dental Society,Chicago Midwinter,CDS,MWM,Continuing Education,Dental Convention,Dental Show
